a:50:{i:1190978;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190978";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:38:"Tribute to the ones that inspired him.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329016";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203290166";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1190979;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190979";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:55:"Yes but names like this doesn&#039;t exist in Equestria";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329052";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203290568";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1190985;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190985";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:196:"I am aware but we have a lot of these kinds of names among many ponies. Shaze&#039;s don&#039;t exist, Neither do Zeus&#039;s or Anna&#039;s, Dan&#039;s or Felicities... What did I do wrong Jason?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329117";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203291178";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1190989;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190989";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:350:"Daniel &quot;Cobalt&quot;, Felicity &quot;Rose&quot; but I digress. It&#039;s nothing you did wrong, but I just don&#039;t understand this character concept and why it has to be something anime inspired. There has been a lot of that and it&#039;s honestly a tad irksome. This is just friendly criticism. I figured you can handle me sharing an opinon.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329287";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203292924";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1190991;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190991";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:184:"An opinion I can handle and accept, His theme was inspired by Hoops who is an actual Character, the anime just helped add substance. I just felt like you were attacking me over this...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329468";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203294694";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1190995;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190995";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:130:"I am sorry. It has been a very stressful Time Jason. I had to call the cops on my own uncle after he did something unforgivable...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329654";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203296553";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1190999;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1190999";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:475:"If this was an attack I&#039;d just say mean crap to you including ad hominem&#039;s that aren&#039;t related to your ability to devise a character. Really all this is that I&#039;ve noticed how you build a character. You make often a lot of direct references to an anime characters or concepts (such as this Eevee). As for the other thing, I&#039;m sorry to hear your troubles with family have sprung up again. What ever it was I know you did not make that decision lightly.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329772";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203297777";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191000;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191000";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:272:"It really was not... And yes, you are right, I am heavily inspired by concepts, often Anime, songs from music, but I do my very best to make them pony before I try anything. And of course it was not easy... I mean... if you can&#039;t trust your family... what do you got?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420329866";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203298667";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191008;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191008";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:99:"To put a bad story short. I have no home to return to in oregon anymore like I had thought I did...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330253";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203302543";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191009;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191009";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:1348:"As someone who had a thief in the family I understand. But back to the original point. I guess part of me is that I want to see if you can make a truly original character. The vast majority of characters you&#039;ve made were very much inspired by previously created ideas or concepts. There are a few that I am certain aren&#039;t but still I never see them as much such as Aaricia. In fact I feel your most successful character in terms of having a variety of players to meet him, interact with them, to create and participate in stories etc... Has been Sonic Blitz. Now, I&#039;m very much aware how he was inspired by Sonic and Tails (If I am wrong on that do call me out) Still during that time when he was still a new concept I noticed how when Midknighthearts was acting up and being a bratty little **** towards everyone and including you I noticed the way you played sonic suddenly shifted from being a bit of a braggart and competitive kid to a heartfilled and passionate one who wanted nothing more then his peers and family to be proud of him. It was as if you wanted to show to everyone &quot;I&#039;m not like this guy! I have a sense of purpose with my characters outside of attention&quot; which really was when I noticed a lot of players enjoyed Sonic the most. I be thrilled to see that same kind of passion in a character again. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330289";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203302944";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191014;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191014";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:405:"Sonic was actually not inspired by Sonic and Tails, even tho I know it is very likely. Sonic was my first True OC, I watched the show and saw so much of myself in Rainbow Dash that I thought. &quot;What if I was a pegasus?&quot; And made Sonic Blitz from that. Honestly Jason, I would love to have that again. and I really think Ariel could be that character for me if I get some more chances to play him.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330502";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203305031";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191021;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191021";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:176:"Sure thing, as for Tetsuya? I guess small edits could help him be more well rounded. Including a new picture maybe. For now like you said I understand it&#039;s a place holder.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330707";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203307120";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191022;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191022";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:83:"If you need help with those edits or finding additional input hit me up for a chat.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330724";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203307289";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191023;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191023";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:177:"I will indeed get a new picture and soon. And I am always open for sit down to help with my characters. I appreciate your help, even if I can come off as ungrateful, I am sorry.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330781";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203307819";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191025;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191025";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:133:"No your fine. I&#039;m just glad you can be civil with me on this stuff. After all, I wanna help ya. Both as a guide and as a friend.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330839";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203308445";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191027;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191027";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1150";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:183:"And I love you Jason. I think I need a fresh OC to start over with. Really get down to my roots again. With Sonic I had just finished the first season of MLP so I was totally into it.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420330908";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#914900";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203309089";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffd16e";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191028;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191028";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Tetsuya_Taiga";s:4:"text";s:154:"Maybe you need to watch some episodes again. Hmm... You know what could be good? Hosting viewing parties... Perhaps we can organize something for the site";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420331064";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203310693";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";